Simple Rule Based AI Agent (No LLM)
This project is  built using FastAPI + PostgreSQL without using any LLM


Setup database:
used postgresql
    1.replace with your database name
    2.replace with your postgresql password

Table auto-creates:
    id INTEGER SERIAL
    key TEXT UNIQUE
    value TEXT unique


Run Instructions
1.Install dependencies
    pip install fastapi uvicorn psycopg2 pydantic python-dotenv


2.Start the server
    uvicorn main:app --reload



To Test the api use PostMan (http://127.0.0.1:8000/agent/read_query)or fastApi swagger Ui (http://127.0.0.1:8000/docs)

POST /agent/read_query

save memory:

    {
    "text": "Remember my cat name is Fluffy"
    }


    Response:

                {
                    "original prompt": "remember my bike's name is KTM",
                    "Choosen tool": "memory_save",
                    "tool_input": {
                        "key": "bike's name",
                        "Value": "ktm"
                    },
                    "response": {
                        "key": "bike's name",
                        "value": "ktm"
                    }
                }


Reterive Memory:
    {
    "text": "What is my cat name?"
    }

    Response:

                {
                    "original prompt": "what is my bike's name ?",
                    "Choosen tool": "memory_read",
                    "tool_input": "bike's name",
                    "response": {
                        "key": "bike's name",
                        "value": "ktm"
                    }
                }


Calculate:
    {
    "text": "What is 10 plus 5"
    }


    Response:

            {
                "original prompt": "what is 10 plus 5",
                "Choosen tool": "Calculator",
                "tool_input": "what is 10 plus 5",
                "response": {
                    "expression": "10+5",
                    "Result": 15
                }
            }



